{"tid":2195811,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚黃 紅燒牛肉麵","createTime":"2020-09-09T11:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T12:43:22.000Z","uid":200063,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8e906715e57fbd380cad75a3fc4d213856dac5","tid":2195811,"uid":200063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"旺角阿木台灣麵 <br />\n紅燒牛肉麵$69 轉手工關廟麵+$3<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DjFQ1X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DjFQ1X.png&h=6fa5eb73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯底尚好，飲落都有牛肉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，飲完喉嚨唔算c伏，但起碼唔會口渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有四大塊牛𦟌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，實際比張相影落多，而且每塊都好腍好入味，正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麵底係成碗麵最大敗筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就算轉左關廟麵，麵底依然太腍，咬口欠奉，更遑論麵粉香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總括而言，除左麵底，其他都係水準以上，牛肉更加係出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ea55741295bad410e12cec2cf78fbb6c64f22f","tid":2195811,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"咪推<br />\n愈黎愈多人排<br />\n我點食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73e85b9abaea3404211a10f1977a935d9be82b1","tid":2195811,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"GCHI 黃店"},{"pid":"d6d280073d44b996367e03643b4e4e17597229f0","tid":2195811,"uid":200063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ea55741295bad410e12cec2cf78fbb6c64f22f","tid":2195811,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"咪推<br />\n愈黎愈